description:
What if learning to code felt as addictive as scrolling your phone, but made you money and changed your life for the better instead of wasting time? In this video, I’ll show you exactly how I hacked my brain to fall in love with coding (and how that nerdy addiction turned into a six-figure career).

🌐 Coursera's Courses

→ IBM Software Developer Certificate: https://imp.i384100.net/c/6100130/3078145/14726

🧑‍💻 SWE Launchpad
Learn How to break Into tech with practical resources, job prep guidance, and real industry insights you won’t find in school. Join the waitlist to be the first to know when we open the doors!
→ https://swelaunchpad.com

✉️ TECH NEWSLETTER
Discover the latest tech trends shaping the industry, unlock career tips, and access exclusive resources to stay competitive in tech. 
→ https://sajjaad.substack.com/

💻 LEARN TO CODE
Learn to code with bite-sized projects and an AI-bot to help answer your ?'s. I recommend you start with their python module, then check out java and javascript.
→ https://coddy.tech/ (FREE, but you can use the code SAJYT for 20% off of premium features!)
